&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Country Italian Restaurant &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This two-story restaurant is located in Zhukovka, where inhabitants are very familiar with the cozy atmosphere of a Tuscan villa. The brickwork, oak flooring, frescoes on the ceiling, a fireplace, wicker chairs, shelves with cans of homemade pickles and jams, along with wood stoves &amp;#8211; one for pizza, and one for meat and fish all combined, make this the perfect place to take a quick trip to Italy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At&lt;em&gt; Osteria Di Campagna&lt;/em&gt;, traditional dishes from almost all regions of Italy are presented in the original interpretation by&nbsp;our chef. Set on its own culinary manufactory, produced here are delicious pastries, handmade pasta, jams, pickles, fruit drinks, cordials and liqueurs. Also, if guests do&nbsp;not have time to sit for breakfast or lunch, it is always possible to buy prepared meals for takeaway.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
